    "We adopt a strong uniform fuzzy partition on the features with five triangular fuzzy sets, as shown in Fig. 1.",
    "The choice of five fuzzy set is driven by the indication of the specialized literature and by the pursuit of a reasonable trade-off between model complexity Fig. 4 A schematic overview of the federated feature selection procedure.",
